          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "A few milligrams of (highly enriched) 124Sn isotope",
                "were evaporated using an \"EDWARDS E306A\" vacuum",
                "coating unit equipped with a molybdenum boat heater",
                "on 20. mu-m thick pure aluminum foils of 11.0 mm",
                "diam. supported in a target holder. After",
                "evaporation, each sample is covered by a 12. mu-m",
                "thick Al foil in order to prevent scratching of the",
                "evaporated Sn film. Two natural tin foils are",
                "enclosed in the stack, and the foils are encapsulated",
                "from both sides with 12.0 mu-m thick Al foils.",
                "Abundance (%) of tin isotopes",
                "isotope     natural sample        enriched sample",
                "Sn-112      0.97                  0.087",
                "Sn-114      0.66                  0.391",
                "Sn-115      0.34                  1.553",
                "Sn-116      14.54                 0.920",
                "Sn-117      7.68                  0.589",
                "Sn-118      24.22                 3.339",
                "Sn-119      8.59                  1.070",
                "Sn-120      32.58                 3.692",
                "Sn-122      4.63                  2.232",
                "Sn-124      5.79                  86.127"
              ]
            }
          ],
